E[X_i]=np=\frac34
\text{Var}(X_i)=np(1-p)=\frac9{16}
 X_i \sim \text{Binom}\left(n=3,~p=\frac14\right) \qquad \text{for} \qquad 1 \le i \le 4, 
W = 2X_1 - 3X_2 - 2X_4
